text: Baishevo () is a rural locality (a village) and the administrative center of Baishevsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 431 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 97 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Baishevo, Zianchurinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
